Package: analDTM
Type: Package
Title: Providing Some Specific Analyzing Functions For The IOM DTM Database
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Bouke Pieter", "Ottow", email = "boukepieter@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Bouke Pieter Ottow <bouke.pieter-ottow@reach-initiative.org>
Description: Providing Some Specific Analyzing Functions For The IOM DTM Database. Taking the IOM DTM database
    as start and perform some analysis, mainly calculating changes between different rounds and disaggregating
    to different administrative levels. It also provides a shiny dashboard and outputs with plotly and leaflet.
